## Imports

### React / TypeScript

```typescript
// CORRECT — named imports from playbook-ui package
import { Button, Card, Flex, Title, Body } from "playbook-ui"

// CORRECT — chart components (rarely needed)
import { PbCircleChart } from "playbook-ui/charts"

// WRONG — never use relative paths or other UI packages
import { Button } from "./components/playbook"
import { Button } from "./components/ui/button"
```

### ERB / Rails

```erb
<%# CORRECT — pb_rails helper with props hash %>
<%= pb_rails("button", props: { text: "Submit", variant: "primary" }) %>

<%# CORRECT — sub-components use slash notation %>
<%= pb_rails("card/card_header", props: { padding: "sm" }) do %>
  <%= pb_rails("title", props: { text: "Header", size: 4 }) %>
<% end %>

<%# WRONG — raw HTML %>
<button class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
```

