## React vs ERB Naming

| Concept | React (camelCase) | ERB (snake_case) |
|---------|-------------------|-------------------|
| Spacing | `marginBottom="md"` | `margin_bottom: "md"` |
| Padding shorthand | `paddingX="lg"` | `padding_x: "lg"` |
| Justify (Flex prop) | `justify="between"` | `justify: "between"` |
| Justify (spec/global) | `"spaceBetween"` → use `"between"` | `"spaceBetween"` → use `"between"` |
| Required indicator | `requiredIndicator` | `required_indicator: true` |
| Text content | JSX children | `text: "value"` or block |
| htmlOptions | `htmlOptions={{ style: {...} }}` | `html_options: { style: "..." }` inside `props:` |
| **Components** | | |
| Text field | `<TextInput />` | `pb_rails("text_input")` |
| Multi-select card | `<SelectableCard>` | `pb_rails("selectable_card")` |
| Input group | `<FormGroup>` | `pb_rails("form_group")` |
| Divider | `<SectionSeparator>` | `pb_rails("section_separator")` |
| Inline loader | `<LoadingInline>` | `pb_rails("loading_inline")` |
| **Sub-components** | | |
| Nav item | `<NavItem>` | `pb_rails("nav/item")` |
| Card header | `<Card.Header>` | `pb_rails("card/card_header")` |
| Table head | `<Table.Head>` | `pb_rails("table/table_head")` |
| Table row | `<Table.Row>` | `pb_rails("table/table_row")` |
| Table header | `<Table.Header>` | `pb_rails("table/table_header")` |
| Table cell | `<Table.Cell>` | `pb_rails("table/table_cell")` |
| Dialog header | `<Dialog.Header>` | `pb_rails("dialog/dialog_header")` |
| Flex child | `<FlexItem>` | `pb_rails("flex/flex_item")` |
| Breadcrumb item | `<BreadCrumbItem>` | `pb_rails("bread_crumbs/bread_crumb_item")` |

