## Component Selection Guide

### Typography

| Need | Component | Key Props |
|------|-----------|-----------|
| Page/section heading | `Title` | size: 1–4 (3 = page, 4 = card) |
| Paragraph text | `Body` | color: default / light / lighter |
| Small label/timestamp | `Caption` | color, size |
| Uppercase metadata | `Detail` | bold |

### Layout

| Need | Component | Notes |
|------|-----------|-------|
| Flexbox layout | `Flex` | Primary layout tool |
| Flex child wrapper | `FlexItem` | Only when you need a dedicated flex child with no other component |
| Content container | `Card` | Use padding prop |
| Page structure | `Layout` | With .Side / .Body / .Header |
| Divider line | `SectionSeparator` | Between sections |

**`flex` global prop vs `Flex` component vs `FlexItem`** — these are three distinct things:

| Concept | What it is | When to use |
|---------|-----------|-------------|
| `Flex` | **Component** — flexbox container | Wrapping children in a flex layout |
| `FlexItem` | **Component** — dedicated flex child | Only when no other component wraps the content |
| `flex` | **Global prop** — works on ANY component | Sizing a child within a Flex parent |

The `flex` global prop can be applied directly to `Card`, `Flex`, `Body`, `TextInput`, etc. You do NOT need `FlexItem` to use flex ratios:

```tsx
// CORRECT — flex global prop directly on components (props in A-Z order)
<Flex gap="md" orientation="row">
  <Card flex="2" padding="md">{/* 40% */}</Card>
  <Flex flex="3" orientation="column">{/* 60% */}</Flex>
</Flex>

// ALSO VALID — FlexItem when no other component wraps the content
<Flex orientation="row">
  <FlexItem flex="3">{/* just text or mixed content */}</FlexItem>
  <FlexItem flex="2">{/* just text or mixed content */}</FlexItem>
</Flex>
```

```erb
<%# ERB — flex global prop directly on components %>
<%= pb_rails("flex", props: { orientation: "row", gap: "md" }) do %>
  <%= pb_rails("card", props: { flex: "2", padding: "md" }) do %>...<% end %>
  <%= pb_rails("flex", props: { flex: "3", orientation: "column" }) do %>...<% end %>
<% end %>
```

### Actions & Navigation

| Need | Component | Notes |
|------|-----------|-------|
| Action button | `Button` | Max 1 primary per section |
| Text link | `Link` | For navigation |
| Tab navigation | `Nav` | horizontal prop for tabs |
| Sidebar nav | `Nav` | Vertical with icons |
| Page hierarchy | `BreadCrumbs` | |
| Filter toggles | `Pill` | Not Badge |

### Forms

| Need | Component | Notes |
|------|-----------|-------|
| Text field | `TextInput` | Always include label |
| Dropdown (4+ options) | `Select` | |
| Multi-line text | `Textarea` | |
| Boolean/multi-select | `Checkbox` | |
| Single choice (2–3) | `Radio` | Use Select for 4+ |
| On/off switch | `Toggle` | Not Checkbox |
| Date entry | `DatePicker` | |
| Autocomplete search | `Typeahead` | |

### Data Display

| Need | Component | Notes |
|------|-----------|-------|
| Tabular data | `Table` | Wrap in Card padding="none" |
| Simple list | `List` | With List.Item |
| Label + value pair | `LabelValue` | Read-only data |
| Numeric metric | `StatValue` | Dashboard stats |

### Feedback & Indicators

| Need | Component | Notes |
|------|-----------|-------|
| User avatar | `Avatar` | Always include name |
| Status tag | `Badge` | variant for color |
| Icon | `Icon` | Font Awesome names |
| Modal | `Dialog` | With Header / Body / Footer |
| Spinner | `Loading` / `LoadingInline` | |
| Tooltip | `Tooltip` | |
| Toast | `FixedConfirmationToast` | |

### Charts (rarely needed in Nitro)

| Need | Import |
|------|--------|
| `PbCircleChart`, `PbBarGraph`, `PbLineGraph`, `PbGaugeChart` | `"playbook-ui/charts"` |

